description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Beginners Stretching Routine (15 minutes) - PHYSIO GUIDED home workout' from the channel Michelle Kenway.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Beginners home workout stretching routine suitable for all levels and guided by Physio Michelle from https://www.pelvicexercises.com.au This gentle whole body stretching routine relieves muscle tension and includes body safe stretches for all levels including beginners. I hope you enjoy and relax with this home stretching routine!

#WithMe #exerciseforbeginners #homeworkout

This 15 minute guided stretching routine is a home workout to exercise along with. No equipment is required other than a towel and cushion to support your body for the lying down stretches. The seated stretches release muscle tension and improve general flexibility in the neck, chest and shoulders. The kneeling and lying down stretches help you release tight muscles in you upper and lower back, buttocks and hips. All the stretches should feel comfortable and pain free. The routine concludes with deep breathing exercises to help you relax at home.
